    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Rings used to say the Christian rosary prayer beads. The surface of the ring is marked with a decade, ten beads or protruding knobs and a cross, to serve as counters to track number of prayers said.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
